  "title": "Medical Social Worker (GOVT/West) - up to $5k #HAO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $5000</p><p>Working Days & Hours: Mon-Fri Office Hours</p><p>Location: Kent Ridge</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>•\tTo assess for mental health issues, provide case formulation and recommendations for treatment.</p><p>•\tTo provide appropriate counseling / psychotherapy for identified inpatients and outpatients.</p><p>•\tTo contribute, as part of an inter-disciplinary team, in the overall care plan for the patient.</p><p>•\tAs part of an inter-disciplinary team, to facilitate transition to adult-care.</p><p>•\tTo develop or improve on workflow for better patient care.</p><p>•\tTo initiate and implement new psycho-social programmes</p><p>•\tTo assist in the development of materials for teaching and training.</p><p>•\tProvide in-service training for department staff as needed.</p><p>Job Requirements: Min Degree in Social Work or similar w min 2-3 yrs of relevant experience</p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p>allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>",
